Lawyer Ghost: Hello again, and thanks for believing in me.
Lawyer Ghost: Even though I've been unsure of a lot of things since I got here, I know I want to be a lawyer.
Lawyer Ghost: I have all the time in the world to solve cases here, so I don't need to push myself the way I did back then.
<<emotionChange None Sparkles>>
Lawyer Ghost: This is a new world, where justice is untouched by corruption - all I have to do is ensure that ghosts can get the justice they deserve.
Lawyer Ghost: Dog Ghost can be my partner attorney, the ace up my sleeve. With his distinct sense of smell and my deduction skills, we'll be unstoppable!
Lawyer Ghost: We'll restore justice to humanity the way the creation of the law intended to.
<<emotionChange None None>>
Lawyer Ghost: I truly can't wait - thanks for listening to me, even if I just blabbed at you like you were my therapist. It means a lot to me.
<<emotionChange None Flowers>>
Lawyer Ghost: Now, go serve your other customers - I'm sure you'll help them as much as you've helped me.
<<emotionChange None None>>
